RelatedSentence: In 2007 , Congress passed the Energy Independence and Security Act , which created the Renewable Fuel Standard .
In 2007 , Congress passed the Energy Independence and Security Act , which created the Renewable Fuel Standard .
Essentially , what that did was to mandate that , by 2009 , all gasoline in the U.S. contain 10 percent renewable fuels .
